'''George Gordon Edington''', [[Order of the British Empire|CBE]], [[RICS|FRICS]], [[Royal Society of Arts|FRSA]] (born 7 September 1945), known as '''Gordon Edington''', is a London-born businessman, and writer. He has been with the British Property Federation (since May 1997) as Vice President (formerly President), and is the Group Property Director of BAA Airports Ltd (since 1991).<ref>[http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=804046&ticker=LLC:AU&previousCapId=704861&previousTitle=MAN%20GROUP%20PLC Edington profile at ''Businessweek'']</ref>

