In 1987, Montena D.L. published two books featuring the Care Bears: ''Juego con los Osos Amorosos'' ({{ISBN|84-397-1099-2}})<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/juega-con-los-osos-amorosos/oclc/434849587|title=Catalog information for ''Juega con los Osos Amorosos''|accessdate=August 10, 2010|work=WorldCat|publisher=Online Computer Library Center (OCLC)}}</ref> and ''Dónde, cómo, qué''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldcat.org/title/donde-como-que/oclc/21389898|title=Catalog information for ''Dónde, cómo, qué''|accessdate=August 10, 2010|work=WorldCat|publisher=Online Computer Library Center (OCLC)}}</ref>  That same year, Madrid's Mondadori published ''Feliz cumpleaños, Osos Amorosos''.<ref>{{cite book| title = Libros en Venta en Hispanoamérica y España| url = https://books.google.com/?id=BTdYAAAAMAAJ| volume = 3| page = 1487 |year=1992|accessdate=September 4, 2010|publisher=[[R.R. Bowker]]}}</ref>

